              "free_text": [
                " Due to the absence of",
                "high energy radioactive sources the fullenergy-peak",
                "efficiency of the AFRODITE array was measured at a",
                "gamma-ray energy of 15 MeV with the reaction of 66 MeV",
                "protons on a carbon target.",
                "The beam current was monitored with a Faraday cup and",
                "integrated for each run."
              ]
            }
