            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " High-energy gamma-rays following proton capture",
                "were detected with the AFRODITE germanium detector",
                "array, which consisted of eight Ge clover detectors",
                "surrounded by the BGO antiCompton shields. Four",
                "detectors at 90 degr. and four at 135. degr."
              ]
